snippet.title: Amber Meets Not Amber
snippet.description:
This is a non grounded video of the first episode of Not Amber Get Grounded Series.

Plot:
On one relaxing day, Amber is chilling on the armchair thinking about what she is going to do today. She heard the doorbell ringing, Amber went to go answer the door. When Amber opened the front door, she got to meet her not clone Not Amber for the first time. When Evil Amber walked into the living room, Evil Amber also got to meet Not Amber for the first time and became troublemaking roommates together. Evil Amber and Not Amber went to their room and play video games for awhile.

Hope you enjoy the show?! 🎬🎥
